1/4/2025
#1 - Title: Improve visibility of left/right menu navigation buttons

Website Tested:
https://www.jollibee.com.ph/menu

Type:
UI/UX Improvement / Enhancement

Current Behavior:
The left (<) and right (>) navigation buttons on the menu section are functional but have a low-visibility color that blends into the background.

Suggestion / Improvement:
Change the color of the left and right navigation buttons to red to match Jollibee’s brand theme and improve visibility.

Expected Improvement:

Navigation buttons are easier to see

Better user experience, especially for first-time users

Improved visual consistency with the website’s red theme

Environment:

Device: Desktop 

#2 - Title: Add slide (drag/swipe) functionality to menu navigation

Website Tested:
https://www.jollibee.com.ph/menu

Type:
UI/UX Improvement / Enhancement

Current Behavior:
The menu section can only be navigated using the left (<) and right (>) buttons. There is no slide (drag or swipe) functionality available for users.

Suggestion / Improvement:
Add slide functionality that allows users to drag or swipe left and right to navigate through the menu items.

Expected Improvement:

Easier and more intuitive navigation

Improved user experience for desktop and touch-enabled devices

Faster browsing of menu items

Environment:

Device: Desktop

