1/5/2025

#6 Title- Improve Overall Website Design and Professional Look

Website

https://mcdonalds.com.ph/our-food

Type

UI/UX Improvement / Enhancement

Environment

Device: Desktop

Browser: All major desktop browsers

Current Behavior

The current website design looks outdated and inconsistent.

UI elements (layout, spacing, colors, typography) do not follow a modern or professional design standard.

User experience feels cluttered and lacks clear visual hierarchy.

Issue

The website’s overall design does not reflect a professional, polished brand experience, which may reduce user trust and engagement.

Suggested Improvements

Redesign the entire UI with a modern and clean layout.

Improve typography, color scheme, spacing, and alignment.

Ensure consistent design components (buttons, cards, forms, icons).

Improve navigation clarity and visual hierarchy.

Add useful UI features such as:

Better product layout and filtering

Clear call-to-action buttons

Improved responsiveness for different screen sizes

Follow modern UI/UX best practices.

Expected Result

The website should look more professional, modern, and visually appealing.

Improved usability and user experience on desktop.

Increased user trust and engagement.

Priority - Critical 

